<p>The selection is smaller but safer. Apps are vetted by Wix. Conflicts are rare. But you cannot replicate the depth of WordPress SEO plugins.</p>
<h3>Verdict: SEO Tools</h3>
<p><strong>WordPress wins on depth.</strong> The plugin ecosystem is unmatched. <strong>Wix wins on simplicity.</strong> Fewer choices mean less room for error.</p>
